 Changes:

Merge pull request #64 from TJEhrenzell/master

Fixed .srdf file

Increased stalled_threshold in autonomous navigation to match the change in
orient2 node. This will result in the new recovery behavior being used
instead.

Created new recovery behavior for the move_base package and implemented in the launch files.
Updated the stalled_threshold in the orient2 node to be much larger so the new recovery
behavior should be used instead. These subroutines will likely be removed when we move
to the updated state machine with more individual nodes.
Added a 1 second wait in the initialization of move_arm_topic.py to help with crashing
issues on my machine.
